    "long_instructions": "### Change the Number of Times the Code will Repeat\r\nEvie is making a song and she wants the Drum Beat Disco sound to loop twice. She also wants the Crackle sound to play every measure the Drum Beat Disco plays. \r\n\r\nChange the numbers in each repeat block to match Evie’s vision. \r\n\r\n![](https://images.code.org/569ccfce7ff4710f7139dce5b0e94272-image-1741813610662.06.46 PM.png)",
